{"tid":695954,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇身邊既人生活多姿多彩而自己就垃撚圾","createTime":"2018-06-09T15:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T08:11:38.000Z","uid":139907,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbd367a6d76e6893e9cca738a97d79166f875ad","tid":695954,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"屌你個閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就做D男性主導行業既（我=/=男，自己諗）<br />\n身邊D囡囡 得閒就講下扮靚／咩餐廳環境好／拍拖點點點／約姊妹／搞生日party <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我份工要一星期返六日，同埋要夜晚返學（一星期3-4晚）<br />\n平時都無咩時間約朋友（已經接近無朋友<br />\n我都好想似返個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁既生活我好受不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但要堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想匿埋喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解人地咁開開心心豬"},{"pid":"fc05497224ce42aa620d5044186bc1e0a02bad11","tid":695954,"uid":51250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"屌你噏乜鳩"},{"pid":"1b30f04c673d0597a33886303affa82cb0c344af","tid":695954,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc05497224ce42aa620d5044186bc1e0a02bad11","tid":695954,"uid":51250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"屌你噏乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"9UP下開心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f623f379b79b8ce03ad4fbe560ed54d8d9db294","tid":695954,"uid":63452,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"講得俾你聽，upload 得上ig fb 實係開心嘢<br />\n平時唔開心嗰面你睇唔到啫"},{"pid":"48b87522fbb93360c14bbcd98d8ee50a6f50eee9","tid":695954,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b30f04c673d0597a33886303affa82cb0c344af","tid":695954,"uid